  Doc translations:
	+ Jonh Wendell (pt_BR)
	+ Jorge González (es)
	+ Mario Blättermann (de)

Vinagre 2.27.91
===============

  Features and Fixes

	+ Updated Unix man page (Emilio Monfort).
	+ Improvements in Telepathy tubes (Arnaud Maillet).
	+ Toolbar in full screen mode is now centralized.
	+ Updated documentation (help).

  UI translations:
	+ Alexander Shopov (bg)
	+ Antón Méixome (gl)
	+ Chao-Hsiung Liao (zh_HK) (zh_TW)
	+ Claude Paroz (fr)
	+ Daniel Nylander (sv)
