Vinagre 2.25.92
===============

  Fixes

	+ Improved the authentication dialog.
	+ Allow IPv6 address in command line as well in	the connection dialog.
	The address must be enclosed by square braces, for instance: [::a:b:c:d].
	This is the same syntax used by RealVNC.

  Translations

	+ Ihar Hrachyshka (be@latin)
	+ Joan Duran (ca)
