Vinagre 2.23.3.1
================
  Bugs

	+ Bug #536330 - [build break] libview/autoDrawer.h: No such file or directory

Vinagre 2.23.3
==============
  Features

	+ Bug #522100 - Provide option to leave fullscreen mode. While in fullscreen
	  mode, if you move the mouse to top of window, a toolbar appears.
	+ Now we grab the keyboard automatically when the focus is on Vinagre
	+ Added a gconf option to disable all menu shortcuts. This is useful if
	  you want to get rid of having your key presses being intercepted by Vinagre.
	+ Bug #515816 - Connect dialog should remember Host/Port address.
	  Also reworked 'connect' and 'edit bookmark' dialogs, allowing you to
	  provide some options to the connection, like scaling, fullscreen...
	+ Bug #536111 - Store bookmarks file in XDG data dir (~/.local/share/vinagre).
	  The old file is automatically copied to new location.

  Bugs
    + Bug #531969 - Fix scrolling.
    + Ubuntu #233918 - Persist changes in menu shortcuts.

  Translations
	+ Djihed Afifi (ar)
	+ Jorge González (es)
	+ Ignacio Casal Quinteiro (gl)
	+ Mate Ory (hu)
	+ Kjartan Maraas (nb)
	+ Tino Meinen (nl)
	+ Manoj Kumar Giri (or)

Vinagre 2.23.2
==============
  Features

	+ Bug #490841, Added "Send ctrl-alt-del" option to menu and toolbar (Henrik Holst).
	+ Tell the server to share the connection with other clients (it can be
	disabled through the gconf key "shared_flag").
	+ Bug #530712, Initial support for VEncrypt sessions (Henrik Holst).
	+ Bug #501165, Support for host::port command line syntax (Henrik Holst).
	+ Bug #518351, Don't show tabs when only one connection is open. (you can
	always show tabs with the gconf key "always_show_tabs".
	+ Bug #519145, Added unique instance behavior. Added a new command line
	option, "--new-window" if you want to use another vinagre window.
	+ Depends on gtk-vnc 0.3.6.

  Fixes

	+ Bug #531593, don't distribute vinagre-enums.[hc].
	+ Bug #530582, handles correctly the clipboard.

  Translations

	+ Jorge González (es)
	+ Ivar Smolin (et)
	+ Ignacio Casal Quinteiro (gl)
	+ Mark Krapivner (he)
	+ Kjartan Maraas (nb)

Vinagre 2.23.1
==============
  Features

	+ Bug #476942, initial support to scaling, see README file for details.
	+ Bug #512918, modified the side panel, to show avahi-discovered machines.
	+ New debug stuff, added the command line option: --gtk-vnc-debug
	+ Bug #509945, provides a 'read-only' mode.
	+ Mandatory dependency on avahi >= 0.6.22

  Fixes

	+ Several minor fixes

  Translations

	+ Simos Xenitellis (el)
	+ Jorge González (es)
	+ Mark Krapivner (he)
	+ Erdal Ronahi (ku)
	+ Kjartan Maraas (nb)
	+ Eskild Hustvedt (nn)
	+ Amanpreet Singh Alam (pa)
	+ Laurent Dhima (sq)
	+ Daniel Nylander (sv)

