Vinagre 0.4
===========

  Features

	+ Store vnc passwords in gnome-keyring
	+ Support clipboard copy and paste
	+ We have our own icon, thanks to Vinicius Depizzol
	+ Basic support to open .vnc files
	+ Keep track of recent connections (Menu Places->Recent Documents)
	+ Lots of minor fixes
	+ Depends on gtk-vnc 0.3

  Translations

	+ Djihed Afifi (ar)
	+ Alexander Shopov (bg)
	+ Joan Duran (ca)
	+ Andre Klapper (de)
	+ Jorge González (es)
	+ Ilkka Tuohela (fi)
	+ Claude Paroz (fr)
	+ Ignacio Casal Quinteiro (gl)
	+ Gabor Kelemen (hu)
	+ Andrea Zagli (it)
	+ Kjartan Maraas (nb)
	+ Reinout van Schouwen (nl)
	+ Yannig Marchegay (Kokoyaya) (oc)
	+ Vladimir Melo and Og Maciel (pt_BR)
	+ W.H. Kalpa Pathum (si)
	+ Matej Urbančič (sl)
	+ Daniel Nylander (sv)

Vinagre 0.3
===========

  Features

    + Shows a message dialog when the connection is lost
    + Added command line parsing, now you can call 'vinagre <host:port>'
    + Added 'Take a Screenshot' feature
    + Shows tooltips on statusbar
    + Shows a error message when the auth fails
    + Depends on gtk-vnc 0.2 (is this a feature? :))

  Fixes

    + A lot of small fixes

Vinagre 0.2
===========

 - Initial public alpha quality release
